gitCommit.subject: Fix Playwright test selectors and timeout configuration
gitCommit.body:
Fix Playwright test selectors and timeout configuration

- Replace incorrect v-model selectors with proper DOM element selectors
- Update timeout configuration to allow more time for form interactions
- Add proper wait conditions for Vue.js form initialization

Co-authored-by: intel352 <77607+intel352@users.noreply.github.com>
